caption: My family and I were very well received, in a welcoming environment, of united brothers who have known each other for years, and the pastor's preaching was excellent, the word of God touched us deeply. I recommend!
We feel the fraternal friendship and love of Christ!
A small Baptist Church where they preach from the Bible and take notes from those listening. Warm and cozy for the soul.
Great!!! We appreciate it very much
A place to listen to the Word of the Bible
